data.description: Come take a look at this beautifully remodeled 4 bed, 2 bath home close to Western Schools! 0.47 acre lot and No HOA! This home features Laminate and Tile flooring throughout.  Major updates include roof (2017), GFA (2018), Water Heater (2018), Water Softener (2018), plumbing, electrical, and much more.  The Kitchen includes Samsung Stainless Steel appliances (2018), soft close cabinets & drawers, tile backsplash and Corian countertops.  The Master bedroom offers a huge walk in closet (8.5 x 12.4) with a self opening & closing barn style door.  Enjoy peaceful evenings on the covered 16 x 16 Deck overlooking the backyard surrounded by a privacy fence.  This house is definitely a must see!
